====================================
1. Building
====================================

Pre-requisites:
 - scons
 - git
 - g++ or clang

Command:

$ scons

This will build the client, server, and coordinator.

$ scons -c

This command cleans the build.

For custom build environments you can place your configuration variables in
Local.sc.

$ scons --help

Shows the supported configuration parameters with a short description and the
default value.

